_sText:
I'm usually one of those people who looks down their nose at aim_fy maps, but with the release of the beta SDK, it messed up my original cs_infiltrate map, so I played around with the new SDK for awhile, and came up with this.

I wouldn't have uploaded it, but I've seen servers play far worse maps.

P.S. A warning to the beta SDK users: Sometimes the info_player_counterterrorist causes Hammer to crash unexpectadly.  To remove the SDK, take away the -beta sdk from the steam file path and refresh your SDK content.
